<item>
            <title>[WICKET-5631] Allow submitting with POST method for PhantomJS</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/WICKET-5631</link>
                <project id="12310561" key="WICKET">Wicket</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the PhantomJS browser form submit is done using get instead of post due to change &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; since 6.12.0&lt;br/&gt;
This is incorrect and fails with larger requests, PhantomJS only allows a limited get request size. For PhantomJS post must be used as for other browsers.&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;1&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=wicket.git;a=commitdiff;h=f0b251e3&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf?p=wicket.git;a=commitdiff;h=f0b251e3&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
